:0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>民國復興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你返大陸食你既屎la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無野我做咩要返大陸？<br />\n<br />\n仲有你自己的行為比人睇到你自己德行，唔單止令你自己蒙羞，亦令你d同行者蒙羞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食屎啦 生癌五毛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/elh9bu7z \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Felh9bu7z%20&h=611114ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a43a8ba2d7737aff7f6e0a33d9223a41078656cf","tid":401173,"uid":97503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"依家個社會係咪一定非黑即白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底發生左咩事<br />\n人地大可以攞綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔撚理你，依家人哋認為自己有手有腳可以出黎做吓嘢，唔攞綜援。<br />\n攞綜援就係廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔攞就係佢on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家到咁上下年齡就自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好經過老年階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話我係左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該收下皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港有乜事 有乜遊行 我一定出黎撐，我唔撚想共狗搞香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想香港好似以前咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人人過得開開心心<br />\n而唔撚係個個分化自己人，好人壞人乜鳩都屌左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13099956bb39528a750af010dc5476a0e59dc4aa","tid":401173,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:39:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9475dd4d05e0200683827a964718325f9a09f695","tid":401173,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:39:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0840352608cc130ad47ce09dc0df3eed830e6f13","tid":401173,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:41:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d1518169eb59c463c2298ad115b8a32b108035b","tid":401173,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:41:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a96b0c94fbddaecc77d663b18fd63464ba628352","tid":401173,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:44:30.000Z","msg":"你知唔知咩係廢老?<br />\n嗰啲俾奶共議員同政府迫仲讚佢地話中國好香港好。持老賣老靠綜緩仲大大聲話&times;十後唔捱得既老人<br />\n你拎個執紙皮既啊婆黎講做乜鳩？<br />\n你個腦可唔可以唔好咁廢?"},{"pid":"f35f364e6e0c62a01baf1f722bfc7a1490d7985f","tid":401173,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭先睇左眼東張西望，講緊唔再回收紙皮，之後訪問一個執紙皮阿婆，個阿婆話佢唔想申請綜援，因為自己有手有腳，又表示依家唔收紙皮唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇到我心都酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:非打手</blockquote><br />\n配服你係咁大壓力下仍堅持仗義執言的勇氣</blockquote><br />\n配你老母<br />\n咪撚扮野洗底啦柒頭五毛<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w5t734oe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw5t734oe&h=9e98d99e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0891bb5a17a21127f600fd2f415c0f202b4d713b","tid":401173,"uid":140642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:48:56.000Z","msg":"你出post我就真心應你<br />\n<br />\n好多老人家老左冇野做出去執紙皮 但其實户口好多錢<br />\n我有一個近親 十年前守中環 有一晚冬天 有個呀婆係報紙檔死左 係佢身上搵到十萬蚊現金<br />\n<br />\n根本你覺得人地慘只係你片面見到既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多未計佢後生時自己唔儲錢呀 慘既個案一定唔夠衰自己既個案多"}]}